    "# In this example usage of Lagrangian descriptors is illustrated"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "178f9106-e33b-40ee-bff1-d2b24303e1d6",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Import\n",
    "\n",
    "import numpy\n",
    "\n",
    "import jax\n",
    "from jax import jit\n",
    "from jax import vmap\n",
    "\n",
    "# Test symplectic mapping and corresponding inverse\n",
    "\n",
    "from tohubohu.util import forward2D\n",
    "from tohubohu.util import inverse2D\n",
    "\n",
    "# Indicators\n",
    "\n",
    "from tohubohu import rem\n",
    "from tohubohu import exponential\n",
    "from tohubohu import ld\n",
    "\n",
    "# Plotting\n",
    "\n",
    "from matplotlib import pyplot as plt\n",
    "from matplotlib import colormaps\n",
    "\n",
    "cmap = colormaps.get_cmap('viridis')\n",
    "cmap.set_bad(color='lightgray')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "6dc15f40-6afe-49eb-af13-bc37204cb96f",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Set data type\n",
    "\n",
    "jax.config.update(\"jax_enable_x64\", True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "3884b04d-1a59-4989-b24e-1950a9dc8b75",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Set device\n",
    "\n",
    "device, *_ = jax.devices('cpu')\n",
    "jax.config.update('jax_default_device', device)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "57f59a32-3965-40c9-9d89-f515dc5f147e",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "(1002001, 2)"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 5,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Set initial grid\n",
    "\n",
    "n = 1001\n",
    "\n",
    "qs = jax.numpy.linspace(-1.0, 1.0, n)\n",
    "ps = jax.numpy.linspace(-1.0, 1.0, n)\n",
    "xs = jax.numpy.stack(jax.numpy.meshgrid(qs, ps, indexing='ij')).swapaxes(-1, 0).reshape(n*n, -1)\n",
    "xs.shape"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "1e4adb00-fe6d-452b-a232-02d37a78ecb3",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Set indicators\n",
    "\n",
    "length = 2**10\n",
    "\n",
    "level = 1.0E-16\n",
    "knobs = jax.numpy.array([0.47, 0.00])\n",
    "\n",
    "fn_rem = jit(rem(length, forward2D, inverse2D, epsilon=1.0E-16))\n",
    "fn_ld = jit(ld(exponential(length), forward2D, inverse2D))\n",
    "\n",
    "@jit\n",
    "def indicator_rem(x):\n",
    "    return jax.numpy.log10(level + fn_rem(x, knobs))\n",
    "\n",
    "@jit\n",
    "def indicator_ld(x):\n",
    "    return jax.numpy.stack(fn_ld(x, knobs))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "id": "0201741d-2fa9-429c-a72e-9c965b8d12b3",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 800x800 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Evaluate indicator (REM)\n",
    "\n",
    "out = jit(vmap(indicator_rem))(xs).block_until_ready()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Winsorize data\n",
    "\n",
    "data = numpy.array(out)\n",
    "data[data < -15.0] = -15.0\n",
    "data[data > -3.0] = -3.0\n",
    "data = data.reshape(n, n)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Plot \n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))\n",
    "plt.imshow(data, aspect='equal', vmin=-15.0, vmax=-3.0, origin='lower', cmap=cmap, interpolation='nearest', extent=(-1.0, 1.0, -1.0, 1.0))\n",
    "plt.xlabel('q')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('p')\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "id": "c755bbd8-08a5-4893-8485-f98415962355",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 800x800 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},

       "<Figure size 800x800 with 1 Axes>"

     "data": {
      "image/png": "",

       "<Figure size 800x800 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Evaluate indicator (LD)\n",
    "\n",
    "out_a, out_b = jit(vmap(indicator_ld))(xs).T.block_until_ready()\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))\n",
    "plt.imshow(out_a.reshape(n, n), aspect='equal', vmin=0.0, vmax=1.0, origin='lower', cmap=cmap, interpolation='nearest', extent=(-1.0, 1.0, -1.0, 1.0))\n",
    "plt.xlabel('q')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('p')\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))\n",
    "plt.imshow(out_b.reshape(n, n), aspect='equal', vmin=0.0, vmax=1.0, origin='lower', cmap=cmap, interpolation='nearest', extent=(-1.0, 1.0, -1.0, 1.0))\n",
    "plt.xlabel('q')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('p')\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))\n",
    "plt.imshow((out_a + out_b).reshape(n, n), aspect='equal', vmin=0.0, vmax=2.0, origin='lower', cmap=cmap, interpolation='nearest', extent=(-1.0, 1.0, -1.0, 1.0))\n",
    "plt.xlabel('q')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('p')\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
